HOPS Support Scripts (in your $PATH)
------------------------------------

env_check          - provides a quick check that your environment is set up
hops.bash          - can be invoked with --help or --version in addition
                     to being sourced directly to set up your environment
pplot_print        - spools a postscript file to a suitable printer (via lpr)
vhelp              - how you got this help (passed through your pager)
vhelper.sh         - just prints this help to the screen
hops_data_links.pl - creates a data link hierarchy


